(80, 1, '2018-10-19 04:15:46', '2018-10-19 04:15:46', '<div class="col-sm-12">\r\n<h3 class="ct-headline text-center ct-u-marginBottom50"><span class="ct-headline-container ct-u-colorMotive">welcome</span></h3>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox ct-infoBox--type1">\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-media ct-infoBox-media--left">\r\n<figure><img class="ct-infoBox-image--square" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/aboutimage1.png" alt="info box img" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-content">\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-title">\r\n<h3>why choose us?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-text">\r\n\r\nWe are a company that has been involved in distributing fruit and vegetables across America. We employ over 100 employees and we work with over 2,000 farmers in all US states. Our company has been for over three generations , always taking care of the highest possible quality of our crops , so you can fully enjoy our products.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox ct-infoBox--type1">\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-media ct-infoBox-media--right">\r\n<figure><img class="ct-infoBox-image--square" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/aboutimage2.png" alt="info box img" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-content">\r\n<div class="ct-divider ct-divider--big ct-u-marginBottom30"></div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-title">\r\n<h3>why we’re different?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-text">\r\n\r\nIn contrast to our competitors, most appreciate the quality of our products. After a same crop of vegetables and fruits we are also involved in their distribution so you do not care about until the delivery to the store. In addition, we do not stop only on what we already have , but also experimenting with new varieties even hard available in our climate.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox ct-infoBox--type1">\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-media ct-infoBox-media--left">\r\n<figure><img class="ct-infoBox-image--square" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/galleryitem6a.jpg" alt="info box img" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-content">\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-title">\r\n<h3>what to expect?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ct-infoBox-text">\r\nAfter our fruits and vegetables you can expect only the same advantages. Our products are genetically enriched with extra doses of vitamins so that your body will always have supplied the correct dose of vitamins. You can expect also that every day we get better at what we do.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Về chúng tôi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 've-chung-toi', '', '', '2018-10-19 08:51:57', '2018-10-19 08:51:57', '', 0, 'http://themes.mywordpress.com/?page_id=80', 0, 'page', '', 0),
